import React from 'react'


export default function Navigation(props){
    return (
        <Grid item xs={12} container className={classes.root} justify="center">

            <Link to={props.prev} style={{margin: '1%'}}>
                <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" size="large" style={{width: '100px'}}>
                    PREVIOUS    
                </Button>
            </Link>              
                    
            <Link to={props.next} style={{margin: '1%'}}>
                <Button 
                    variant="outlined" 
                    color="primary" 
                    size="large" 
                    style={{width: '100px'}}
                    onClick={() => updateState(name, props)}>
                        NEXT  
                </Button>
            </Link>  
        </Grid>
    )
}
